Note: Test selective import functionality

Import { add, square } from "math_helpers.runa"

Process called "main" takes argc as Integer, argv as Pointer returns Integer:
    Let result1 be add(10, 20)
    Display "10 + 20 = "
    Display result1
    Display "\n"

    Let result2 be square(9)
    Display "9^2 = "
    Display result2
    Display "\n"

    Return 0
End Process
